{"tid":556144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強姦犯涉獄中打傷懲教員","createTime":"2018-02-10T08:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T10:26:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"598a64a5f856d99a3f0ac8d3f70664ccfdb09b4b","tid":556144,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180210/20301106?_ga=2.257393291.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F20301106%3F_ga%3D2.257393291.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435&d=0WKnxho0shvkctxUfybzvZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b66a8416\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180210%2F20301106%3F_ga%3D2.257393291.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435&h=95207959\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180210/20301106?_ga=2.257393291.1662121137.1517898321-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n強姦犯涉獄中打傷懲教員<br />\n<br />\n3,824<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180210/large/10ls3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180210%2Flarge%2F10ls3p3.jpg&h=802183d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】漢能控股外籍前高層因帶27歲及19歲女網友回家侵犯，更奪去其中一人處女身，受審後因強姦及非禮罪成，2015年被判囚8年，法官直斥他是性愛獵食者。他去年於大嶼山石壁監獄服刑時，被指派洗廁所時，涉突出拳毆傷懲教署人員。強姦犯否認一項普通襲擊罪受審，受傷懲教員稱曾叫被告勿吸煙後，被告不再向他打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n比利時籍男被告Laurent Frank（39歲，圖）否認去年9月2日犯案。事主梁志輝（譯音）稱，他指示拿着鮑魚刷的被告「You, clean toilet（你，洗廁所）」。被告遲疑，跟着目露兇光，突由下而上拳打他胸口一下，有洗刷用「沙粉」（去污粉）灑到臉上，令他不適。梁指雙方以往關係和諧，被告會敬禮說「Morning, sir」，但案發前數天叫被告不要吸煙後，被告「對我嘅面口唔同咗」，敬禮不復見。案件本月21日續審。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC5548/17<br />\n■記者伍嘉豪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n無視資產凍結令　經理藐視法庭判囚"},{"pid":"77b12a3171dd9053c357411bae3f176384d73084","tid":556144,"uid":100626,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:55:01.000Z","msg":"啲鬼佬係香港真係以為自己大曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗廁所啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61345dfa8e6f8f9dd677d55de66242548dcb5c81","tid":556144,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/l56P85.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2Fl56P85.gif&h=ad5a6e95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa56724c505fe92abe8b92a9fbbd005f78847d15","tid":556144,"uid":77569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e712138203cac0a0ffbc1d78e84dee3957822868","tid":556144,"uid":98386,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:57:32.000Z","msg":"自己攞黎衰 又唔夠鬼佬抽又要搞個鬼佬 你求其揾隻支那狗或者港柒去洗根本乜事都冇"},{"pid":"a55e7b23da0887325901b0144253278d37974328","tid":556144,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:58:00.000Z","msg":"前高層<br />\n強姦真on9<br />\n大撚把女自動比佢屌啦<br />\n傻鳩"},{"pid":"ff705fb07d8928c98bf05c1820a8aec9f0f2a722","tid":556144,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:58:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"498230c30507213c97e143dd13d033a0c400563f","tid":556144,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T08:58:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"640c5ccac4567019b5fea1312f78d221f5d5638b","tid":556144,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:01:09.000Z","msg":"強姦犯否認一項普通襲擊罪受審，受傷懲教員稱曾叫被告勿吸煙後，被告不再向他打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線文筆"},{"pid":"ad6782fd3f599780c833f7128753c3a9f8b292e0","tid":556144,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T09:01:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前高層<br />\n強姦真on9<br />\n大撚把女自動比佢屌啦<